V=\mathbb{R}^3
T=\{(t,t,0);t\in\mathbb{R}\}
U=\{(x,0,z);x,z\in\mathbb{R}\}
W=\{(0,y,z);y,z\in\mathbb{R}\}
T+(U\cap W)=\{(t,t,z);t,z\in\mathbb{R}\}
(T+U)\cap(T+W)=\mathbb{R}^3
T=\{(x,0,0);x\in\mathbb{R}\}
U=\{(0,y,0);y\in\mathbb{R}\}
W=\{(t,t,0);t\in\mathbb{R}\}
(T+U)\cap W=W
(T\cap W)+(U\cap W)=\{0\}
